%% ThunderaFit — auth flow (complementary diagram)
%% Login + JWT/refresh lifecycle. See src/auth/AGENTS.md for authorization
%% rules and gotchas; this file is only the request/response shape.

sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as "Fastify (src/auth)"
    participant DB as "Postgres (User)"

    C->>API: POST /api/auth/login (email, password)
    API->>DB: find User by email
    API->>API: bcrypt compare passwordHash
    API->>DB: store refreshTokenHash, lastLoginAt
    API-->>C: Set-Cookie: access (JWT, 15min) + refresh (7d), both httpOnly

    Note over C,API: Every subsequent request

    C->>API: request + cookie (access)
    API->>API: verify JWT (cookie takes priority over Authorization header —<br/>prod proxy injects a Google ID token there)
    API-->>C: 200 (or 401 if expired)

    Note over C,API: Access token expired

    C->>API: POST /api/auth/refresh (cookie: refresh)
    API->>DB: compare refresh token hash
    alt hash matches
        API->>DB: rotate — new refreshTokenHash
        API-->>C: new access + refresh cookies
    else hash mismatch (reuse of an old/rotated token)
        API->>DB: invalidate refreshTokenHash (force full re-login)
        API-->>C: 401 — theft/reuse detected
    end
